    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_6468966958480806019.png",
                "key": "迴身箭術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迴身箭術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">疾風示現</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">疾風示現</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>少花費1個<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無色元素</span>，造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>，並且使目標角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">風壓坍陷</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/6f3f1e66aac8d91ecca768d4a7f48e56_6776367532107674832.png",
                "key": "非想風天",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "非想風天"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">赫耀多面體</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/bec3c6e3c0067cc3e0340d50df63f27e_7856658042511218177.png",
                "key": "摶風秘道",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "摶風秘道"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召喚物在場時：</span>敵方角色受到的<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7636508608732916186.png",
                "key": "赫耀多面體",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/7c29f5ce38f0d332fbd3113f1b605a5c_3980621288161691749.png",
                "title": "赫耀多面體"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_4584035024714455582.png",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重擊</span></p><p>我方行動開始前，如果元素骰總數為偶數，則進行的「普通攻擊」將被視為「重擊」。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無色元素</span></p><p>可以用任意類型的元素骰子組合，來支付此類費用。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">風壓坍陷</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>將所附屬角色切換為「出戰角色」。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p><p>（同一方場上最多存在一個此狀態）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1998319653080511780.png",
